{"tid":1663532,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"［Apple已死］iPhone 11 系列需求創新高   中國市場銷售急增 230%","createTime":"2019-10-19T12:50:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T02:34:57.000Z","uid":109923,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c26a7018a2fab854875090bea3f73f9bf1262509","tid":1663532,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T12:50:22.000Z","msg":"每逢中國跟其他國家有任何糾紛，網民都會抵制該國的貨品，現時中美貿易戰仍未解決，抵制美國商品自然鬧得沸沸揚揚。雖然很多網民口中說著抵制美國產品，但新發表的 iPhone 11 系列似乎免疫，根據美國證券公司的分析報告，新 iPhone 在中國大陸市場表現相當出色。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bGigDZF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbGigDZF.jpg&h=ab381ad5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n證券公司 Wedbush 分析師 Dan Ives 日前撰文，表示 iPhone 11 系列三款新機的銷量相當理想，當中以中國大陸的需求最為強勁。投資銀行瑞銀的分析師 Timothy Arcuri 亦有相同睇法，他甚至指大陸市場對 iPhone 11 系列的需求，在上月急增了 230%。新 iPhone 發表導致需求增加是市場正常反應，不過對比起去年發表的 iPhone XS，當時大陸市場的需求只有 110% 的增幅。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWedbush 的報告指售價相對便宜的 iPhone 11，在大陸市場最受歡迎，至於美國市場，消費者最喜愛 iPhone 11 Pro，銷量超過了去年的 iPhone XS 之餘，亦遠超 Apple 的預期。"},{"pid":"11f4bc77402ef9c45ad4a912b76b02751cc6ebe3","tid":1663532,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T12:50:57.000Z","msg":"[1020 行動Post] 香港人真係好痴線！不論組織力、耐力、創意玩到咁！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eovgRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eovgRS</a>"},{"pid":"73d8c0d76d95bedf9bc332e980cec5d7af12faad","tid":1663532,"uid":66365,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T12:53:15.000Z","msg":"奶共既成效發揮了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30cad770486cfef9be8935c10b6d1fbe1f144f13","tid":1663532,"uid":258566,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T13:04:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"07198f16d2966fb28ef2790b463fcdb9164fecbf","tid":1663532,"uid":3032,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"30cad770486cfef9be8935c10b6d1fbe1f144f13","tid":1663532,"uid":258566,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"c